{"tid":845390,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"21歲男師要求口交 　14歲少年吃5次不敢上學","createTime":"2018-10-02T15:08:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T04:09:39.000Z","uid":1426,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2297aceeeb1a565216a2ddd1966927eb0fe89aca","tid":845390,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T15:08:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180712/640_f781776fbbf2ede8f771b91f2a999da8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180712%2F640_f781776fbbf2ede8f771b91f2a999da8.jpg&h=bf9b881e&s={SIZE}\" /> 馬來西亞雪州淡江1所宗教學校，近日傳出14歲男學生，遭21歲男老師多次要求口交，心靈受創不敢上學的事件。<br />\n <br />\n根據大馬《中國報》報導，這名男學生是在今年5月，才剛遠從柔佛家鄉前來入學，沒想到惡夢就開始了，在5-6月間，男老師就多次要求他口交，他一開始曾經拒絕要求，但後來又擔心被老師記恨，就勉強答應了，共幫男老師口交了5次，每次約3分鐘。<br />\n <br />\n報導中說，男學生忍耐了1個多月，在6月26日回到柔佛家裡，才鼓起勇氣告訴家人，自己遭到獸行傷害，飽受壓力不敢再回去學校，父母得知後大驚，連忙帶男學生報警。<br />\n <br />\n（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）"},{"pid":"0f9e23e78b2dd32db91798238aff713905c01941","tid":845390,"uid":2507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T15:12:15.000Z","msg":"gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b53437da419e767dd4f275cd2e0912c260d92f5d","tid":845390,"uid":149566,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T15:27:19.000Z","msg":"張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b91b4d576a17bb3e32f788a994ccde6e873843e2","tid":845390,"uid":116364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T15:35:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3085152e6745239954d9841426d6321b75fa84a7","tid":845390,"uid":205844,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T15:36:16.000Z","msg":"以為新北<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a63250221b3e62ba0eed8f8f3020382d9eace5e8","tid":845390,"uid":59711,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T15:37:05.000Z",